Self-Fueling Machine

	Philosophy

		-
			A self-fueling machine is a machine that can recharge itself using energy from its
			environment.
		-

	Principles

		Sleeping Machine

			-
				A sleeping machine is a self-fueling machine that, while in the field, periodically
				enters an inactive state in order to recharge itself.
			-

		Insomniac machine

			-
				An insomniac machine is a self-fueling machine that can recharge its energy faster
				than it can expend it.
			-